---
import HomeButton from './HomeButton.astro';
---

<section class="home-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="left-column">
        <div class="subsection">
          <h2 style="font-family: 'Averia Serif Libre', serif; font-weight: 400;" class="section-title">Explore the Garden</h2>
          <p>A living ecosystem of ideas, explorations and essays, from emerging seedlings of thought to fully grown trees. Every visit reveals something new.</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <HomeButton href="/garden" variant="secondary" icon="logo">Browse the Garden</HomeButton>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="subsection">
          <h2 class="section-title">Resources & Guides</h2>
          <div class="collections-table">
            <!-- First row: Main resources (2 columns) -->
            <div class="first-row">
              <div class="collection-item">
                <h3 class="item-title">Digital Gardening Guide</h3>
                <p class="item-desc">How to start and maintain your own digital garden</p>
                <a href="/resources/digital-gardening" class="view-link">View Guide</a>
              </div>
              
              <div class="collection-item">
                <h3 class="item-title">Note-Taking Systems</h3>
                <p class="item-desc">A comparison of different approaches to personal knowledge management</p>
                <a href="/resources/note-taking" class="view-link">View Guide</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="right-column">
        <div class="subsection">
          <h2 style="font-family: 'Averia Serif Libre', serif; font-weight: 400;" class="section-title">Hello, I'm KiTTeLSAA</h2>
          <p>
            I'm a Software Engineer and a Digital Anthropologist. Think of it as exploring 
            the human side of the digital world; how we build software, how we use it and
            what it does to the way we learn and share knowledge.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <HomeButton href="/about" variant="primary" icon="arrow">More About Me</HomeButton>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="subsection">
          <h2 style="font-family: 'Averia Serif Libre', serif; font-weight: 400;" class="section-title">Let's Connect</h2>
          <p>Reach out to chat, collaborate on projects or exchange ideas about knowledge systems, Artifitial Intelligence and more at kttlsaa@gmail.com </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  
  .subsection {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .subsection:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .subsection h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .averia-font {
    font-family: var(--font-fun);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .collections-table {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #C0C0C0;
  }
  
  .first-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .collection-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #C0C0C0;
    background-color: var(--color-surface, #fff);
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    margin-top: -1px;
    margin-left: -1px;
  }
  
  .collection-item:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-surface-hover, #f5f5f5);
  }
  
  .item-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: normal;
  }
  
  .item-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted, #666);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .view-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-accent, #FF9B5A);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .view-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .first-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .subscribe-form {
      max-width: none;
    }
    
    .subscribe-form input,
    .subscribe-button {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
</style>
